trans-unit.source: Represents the contents of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_wsc:CallbackContext" name="wsc:CallbackContext" href=""></xref> message header when using a channel that supports the context exchange protocol.
trans-unit.target: Representerer innholdet i den <xref uid="langword_csharp_wsc:CallbackContext" name="wsc:CallbackContext" href=""> </xref> meldingshodet når du bruker en kanal som støtter konteksten exchange-protokollen.

trans-unit.source: The context exchange protocol allows for duplex communication between durable services.
trans-unit.target: Konteksten exchange protokollen tillater duplekskommunikasjon mellom minneoptimaliserte services.
